Reasoning: The paper discusses statistical data analysis, formal learning theory, and learnability from statistical data, which are all topics that fall under the umbrella of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also touches on information theory (cs.IT), statistics (cs.ST), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS) in its discussion of the unique topology on probability measures and the characterization of learnability in the limit.
